name: "azul, parte II", 2021
description:
"Slam da Guilhermina" is a collective on the outskirts of the city of São Paulo that has existed since 2012 promoting reading and spoken poetry every last Friday of the month at Praça Guilhermina. You can check the work on instagram.com/slamdaguilhermina

• shot on Nikon D50 with ARSAT H 1:2 50mm at São Paulo, Brazil.
• find me on Twitter: @miguelzinhe
